text: The food is delicious. So far tasted their Horfun chicken, salted egg chicken and Nasi goreng ikan masin. It was delicious. Recommended for their food.

MAJULAH MCC Makanplace!

IKAN BAKAR is Splendid!
The sambal is a Wow!
I have been to many
Nothing beats yours

Service is Alhamdullillah.
I am placing order again for today and
I am coming with My Galfrens this Friday!

I have been to MCC Makanplace
So Have You?!
Been here for few times. Love the food & their service is good.
Good portion of food given. Price is reasonable. It's tasty as well. Came at 8am and they're already selling lontong, nasi lemak, fried mee, curry puff, etc. Their tea is fragrant and nice.

NEVER EVER buy the $9.00 (NINE DOLLARS) packed beryani from this place!! I really felt cheated by the huge packet only to discovered that 90% of the content was rice, 9% bone (2 pcs of bones wrapped with rempah), 1% the rempah itself. The rest you imagine it yourself of the frustration upon the discovery. Can we call this business as halal?? Idk. WallaHu a'lam bissawab.
Date of purchase: 18 April 2021 for Ramadhan iftar
